{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"毛主席是红太阳","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":12,"day":6}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是红太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两位越南老人以无限喜悦和激动的心情，合写了一首颂诗，表达了越南人民热爱毛主席的真挚情感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒万丈照四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天有你百花放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗青青菜花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天有你秧苗长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民心里乐无疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天有你收成好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄谷粒堆满仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天有你冰雪化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民身上暖洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的恩情永不忘。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}